* output 1 -> shows output from agent 1
* error 1 -> shows errors from agent 1
* errors -> shows all errors

* various flags, especially for main conf.

* seekable ringbuf (reader can seek to beginning or end)

* see fio ( http://linux.die.net/man/1/fio ) for options and ideas.
* see splice(2) for an almost zero-copy data piping between commands.

